Package: et-create-project
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: application for creating empty git project directories
 Helper tool for creating empty project directories. The application will 
 initialize a project directory with a gitignore, readme and a licence file. 
 You may optionally specify if the project will be an npm project ( --npm ) or 
 a dep ( --deb ) project which will add specific files. 